            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Greater Manchester Combined Authority as the Contracting Authority for Greater Manchester Police is tendering for the provision of a Building Services Maintenance and Installation service.</P>
               <P>The contract will cover PPM and Reactive Maintenance including capital projects in the event that replacement installations are required. The contract will include all major mechanical assets such as Boiler Plant, Ventilation Air Handling Plant, Air Conditioning Plant and Fan Coil Units, Building Management Systems and stand-alone Control Systems. Plus routine Statutory Inspection of all associated equipment. Please refer to the specification for more details. The contract will be subject to GMP Terms and Conditions.</P>
               <P>For an initial period of 3 years with the option to extend for a further 2 years subject to performance.</P>
               <P>Estimated Value 1 200 000 GBP Per annum (including project work).</P>
               <P>Projects are subject to requirement.</P>
               <P>No volume or value of orders will be guaranteed in respect of this contract.</P>
